{"title":"向党宣誓","authors":["陈克成"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":9,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"向党宣誓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈克成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗议美国野心狼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拥护我国好主张！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台湾本是中国土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放领土理应当。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我向党委来宣誓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把愤怒化力量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平时奔向红与专，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战时投笔上战场！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}